title: $2 Billion Powerball Ticket Sold in Los Angeles County, Lottery Said
description: The identity of the winner or winners is not yet known, but the California Lottery said it had made its first billionaire. There was a delay in announcing the winning numbers, because of a security issue.
dc:creator: Remy Tumin, Amanda Holpuch and Johnny Diaz
media:description: The Powerball jackpot grew to $1.9 billion after the drawing Saturday night produced no top prize winner.
